					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">For the OS, use an Ubuntu variant. For a bargain-basement SSD, use a suitably fast CF card through a <a href="http://www.addonics.com/products/flash_memory_reader/ad44midecf.asp" class="postlink">CF-to-parallel-ATA adapter</a>.
<br />
<br />"Abandonware" is a myth. To be 100% legal, you have to build a CopyNES and dump your own Game Paks. It'd be easier if the Retrode supported NES, but it doesn't.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
